This map is provided for informational purposes only. While every effort has been made to ensure the accuracy of the information presented, errors or omissions may occur. The data displayed has not been created or verified by me and is sourced directly from the following external providers and updated on their scheduled:

  NB Active Wildfires layer and Burn Ban layer sourced from https://nbdnr.maps.arcgis.com/

  Weather Stations from https://esricanada.maps.arcgis.com/home/item.html?id=38406bada3104e258fc8b42a2a96581a

  VIIRS Hot Spots from https://www.arcgis.com/home/item.html?id=dece90af1a0242dcbf0ca36d30276aa3

  Fire Perimeters from https://services.arcgis.com/wjcPoefzjpzCgffS/ArcGIS/rest/services/Active_Wildfire_Perimeters_in_Canada_View/FeatureServer/0

  Aircraft locations from OpenSky API

  NB Crown Lands from https://geonb.snb.ca/

  Sentinel2C Imagery from https://sentinel.arcgis.com/arcgis/rest/services/Sentinel2/ImageServer

No guarantee is made as to the completeness, currency, or accuracy of this information. Users should verify all information independently before making decisions based on it. Use of this map constitutes acceptance of these terms.
